sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Dev as Developer
    participant NPM as npm scripts
    participant UV as uvicorn
    participant Docs as Swagger UI
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant PT as pytest
    participant RF as ruff
    participant Git as Git and CI

    Note over Dev,PG: Bring up data and server
    Dev->>NPM: npm run db:up
    NPM->>PG: start container, wait until healthy
    Dev->>NPM: npm run backend
    NPM->>UV: uv run uvicorn app.main:app --reload

    loop Inner loop: add an endpoint
        Dev->>UV: add Pydantic schema in app/schemas/
        Dev->>UV: add router in app/routers/
        Dev->>UV: include router in app/main.py under /api
        UV-->>UV: reload restarts on save
        Dev->>Docs: try the endpoint at /docs
        Docs->>UV: POST /api/...
        UV->>PG: query via SQLAlchemy session
        PG-->>UV: rows
        UV-->>Docs: validated JSON response
    end

    Note over Dev,PT: Prove it with tests
    Dev->>PT: add tests in backend/tests/ (in-memory SQLite)
    Dev->>NPM: npm run test:backend
    NPM->>PT: pytest, calls route functions directly
    PT-->>Dev: pass or fail

    Note over Dev,RF: Gate before commit
    Dev->>NPM: npm run lint:backend
    NPM->>RF: ruff check .
    RF-->>Dev: pass or fail

    Dev->>Git: commit, push, open PR
    Git->>Git: Checks workflow: setup, lint, build, test
    Git-->>Dev: green check or failure

    Note over Dev,PG: Changing models? Use the database workflow
